<span id="freeTextContainer5199185282921831545">Learning to Live: An Enemy to Lovers Ugly Cry (The Infinite Love Series, Book 1) by Kira Adams is a YA contemporary romance. It is an emotion inducing read that will require tissues, a strong drink and lots of hugs. This moving, soul wrenching, heartbreaking tale has some delightful, tender and sweet moments. There are a number of hot topics and messages through out that Kira lovingly weaves together. <br/><br/>The story is about two young people Topher &amp; Ciera who come from completely different worlds an</span>
  <span id="freeText5199185282921831545" style="display:none">Learning to Live: An Enemy to Lovers Ugly Cry (The Infinite Love Series, Book 1) by Kira Adams is a YA contemporary romance. It is an emotion inducing read that will require tissues, a strong drink and lots of hugs. This moving, soul wrenching, heartbreaking tale has some delightful, tender and sweet moments. There are a number of hot topics and messages through out that Kira lovingly weaves together. <br /><br />The story is about two young people Topher &amp; Ciera who come from completely different worlds and who have to deal with difficulties, bullying and harassment and the fall out from it. It is also a story of forgiveness and second chances.<br /></span>
